      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an easy entry price. It shows its age and would best suit a buyer looking for practical value, a project opportunity, or an inexpensive second vehicle. Priced with its condition in mind, it represents a straightforward chance to get behind the wheel without overspending.",
