    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little runaround that\u2019s priced for someone who wants affordable wheels without any nonsense. It\u2019s not a showroom car, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option with plenty of life left for the right buyer. Ideal as a cheap daily, learner car, or a handy project to tidy up over time. If you\u2019re after something simple, usable, and easy on the wallet, this one\u2019s worth a look.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong project or budget daily candidate with a willing powertrain, solid road manners, and plenty of life left for the next owner who knows their way around basic upkeep. It starts, runs, and drives, with a chassis that feels usable and a drivetrain that still pulls through the rev range. Cosmetically it shows its age and will want attention, but the fundamentals make it a worthwhile platform for someone looking for inexpensive transportation, a starter build, or a shop-friendly refresh. Priced to move and leave room for improvements.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Honest poor-condition car priced to move. Great budget ride, project, or parts donor. Clean deal. No fluff.",
